  <brief_title>A Extension Study to Evaluate Revusiran (ALN-TTRSC) in Patients With Transthyretin (TTR) Cardiac Amyloidosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2, Open-label Extension Study to Evaluate the Long-Term Safety, Clinical Activity, and Pharmacokinetics of ALN-TTRSC in Patients With Transthyretin (TTR) Cardiac Amyloidosis Who Have Previously Received ALN-TTRSC</official_title>
  <sponsors>
