  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study was to evaluate the safety and clinical activity of long-term
      dosing with revusiran (ALN-TTRSC). Dosing has been discontinued; patients are being
      followed-up for safety.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
